Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.22,0:00:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去趟防火水槽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.17,0:00:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又來了  那可不是女高中生該去的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家路上要順便去趟大工咖啡店嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡整個的運作系統都有了很大的改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對麻衣來說也許有點難懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.77,0:00:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把那裡的各種各樣的事情都教給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻…麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是非對稱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:53.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(375,340)\fs20}Asymmetry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.48,0:00:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  雖然你說的沒錯  但這已經是很強烈的不對稱了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.23,0:00:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經超越了漂亮的界限了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在裝傻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.40,0:01:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探究得太深了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  這好像已經完全不知道意思了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.23,0:01:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上天也是站在麻衣這邊的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:04.96,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(400,400)}日\N常\N之\N68
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的菜色  要怎麼配好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔥好像很便宜  做蔥料理怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是博士討厭吃蔥的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  你看  我抓住了一隻烏鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你都做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做很危險的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被啄傷的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知在何時圍巾就突然不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是烏鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後還請多多賞臉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好它是一隻有禮貌的烏鴉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是烏鴉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到您的稱讚是我的榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它喝草莓牛奶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果會喝的話還真可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚊子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然還幫我們消滅蚊蟲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  這是我應該做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是烏鴉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  阪本先生  你的圍巾上哪兒去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有圍巾的話  就聽不懂它在說什麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來試著聽聽看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像它很想要我的圍巾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你的圍巾吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  難道你把阪本先生的圍巾給烏鴉戴了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣的話阪本先生就太可憐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  我再去做一條
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是餅乾1號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和圍巾沒有半毛錢關係！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問博士  餅乾1號有著什麼樣的機能呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏鴉問得好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會放出火箭拳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼要來一發了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博…博士  差不多該給阪本先生圍…圍巾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為還有左手在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備…發射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把這些傢伙全部殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  今天真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我好像玩笑開過頭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把這個圍巾還給阪本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很短暫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠說人類的語言我真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:06:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏鴉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走  烏鴉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有機會的話  我們再會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家請多多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See  you  again！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏鴉～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然戴著飛走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦不到的啦  課長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法信任我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是完全信任課長的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那麼就請助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  疼疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
