Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在體育館後面挖好了黏著劑陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就用這封信把她約出來騙到陷阱裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我一定要抓住你  東雲名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:20.95,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(90,300)\fad(400,400)}日\N常\N之\N70
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.20,0:13:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到櫻井誠居然是櫻井老師的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我得想辦法問到櫻井老師的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會踢圍棋足球嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  櫻井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你有在交往中的男朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No  future！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼總是這樣  我這種男人真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這種男人真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  沒有倒是沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有倒是沒有啦…  沒有倒是沒有啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:14:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長…長…長出來啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.41,0:14:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長出來啦！  我發達了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的你就視而不見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  你在踢圍棋足球嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有在踢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道老師你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡我們家姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼傻話！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是作為圍棋足球部的學長在和你說話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  你會踢圍棋足球嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在高中可是MVP！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  其實現在我們的圍棋足球部還沒有顧問老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您能來當顧問老師的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於我姐姐的事我會全力協助的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我才沒有喜歡她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您不來當顧問老師的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:14:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就去散佈您喜歡我姐姐的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:14:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來當顧問老師嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不來當呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…  當顧問很麻煩的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大家聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:10.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你這威脅者！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…追上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中之條君在體育館後面被埋住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您能儘快來一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  高崎老師他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中之條他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有被埋住！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  他只是一杆進洞了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他的頭髮都被拔掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我畫上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試試！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎麼回事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起被埋  去管教暴露他人隱私的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是作為教育者…怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣才是教育者啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高崎老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我等著您來當顧問老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可真懂事兒～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安中  要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點趕過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才是教師該做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.70,0:01:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是順勢而行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剃掉別人頭髮終究還是不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:36.37,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,320)\fad(40,400)}體\N育\N館\N後\N2
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正他也不知道是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:43.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊咧  啊咧咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡  這裡是哪裡  好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼  動不了了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  怎麼了怎麼了怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水  水  鯊魚鯊魚  啪哢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯊魚鯊魚  啪庫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就是這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:12.32,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,380)\fs30}琪琪其實是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
