Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
